Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:45.45,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.33,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Aren't you so very cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:56.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're like this,\Nyou look just like a girl, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be even cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.15,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's try some\Nother clothes. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:06.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,A prettier ribbon\Nwould be better, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:08.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:15.03,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! You messed up\Nat the same place again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't like the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:22.21,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was your age, I could play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:24.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's no reason why\Nyou can't play it too, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:25.97,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:45.82,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you can do it. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.85,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.90,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:14.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I said quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akira, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:00.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,White lilies are the\Nsymbol of Mary's virginity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What is "virginity"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you wouldn't know yet, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:11.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that\Nyou aren't dirtied by anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:30.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.04,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's a girls' school like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:39.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if there were only girls,\Nthen it'd be really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.41,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.08,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost taller than you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.03,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:39.76,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.81,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... tell anyone.
