Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.82,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here to take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:27.60,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave your name,\Nnumber and message at the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:38.48,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya, who are you\Nsleeping with tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your sister again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still such a spoiled little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like that part of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.55,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.02,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.66,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.85,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.97,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to say you won't\Nlend me your notes, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:15.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.00,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the library, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that test the day after\Ntomorrow will be a breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.63,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,The rental fee is,\Nyou owe me a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.04,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! That's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:37.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you wearing\Nthat outfit yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:38.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, do you check up on things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.56,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But I DID change my underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.67,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I was\Nwith last night wasn't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a guy from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:58.55,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:02.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?\NIt's okay. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:06.98,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Yoshiko, you were saying\Nhow much you liked Amemiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:11.02,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping around, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:16.41,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't bother you,\Neven though you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.41,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're\Ntrying to say, Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:23.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it doesn't mean anything even\Nif you say "I love you" to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:28.61,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, he's the ultimate sex friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,With him, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:37.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to worry\Nabout others and all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, at the\Nharbor park, I saw Tatsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't tell me\Nyou already knew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:52.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?\NDon't you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:56.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:00.15,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a fool,\NI just believed that he loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.30,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Just steal him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.56,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I don't want him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:09.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Leona.\NHow is it over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's already that chilly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful! Don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't just\Nchat on an international call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's sudden,\Nbut I want you to go to Rome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.41,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,though it'll delay your\Nhomecoming even further.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. I'll fax you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.98,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Amemiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:12.32,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You know my friend,\NKaname, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:13.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She's being cheated on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.59,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname is just too straight-laced.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.80,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the type who thinks you can't\Nhave sex unless you love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:30.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you laugh, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're different?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.08,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.48,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sex doesn't need a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.99,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:47.62,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Amemiya,\NI have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:53.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we make\Nit your place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.63,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:58.33,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...\Nit's always been somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.60,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:03.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Weren't you taking me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,If you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.88,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.43,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Message number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.67,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of a sudden\Nschedule change...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,your sister's\Nhomecoming will be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.81,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to going be\Nnext week, but I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.62,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,End of message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:11.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, how long are you\Ngoing to leave me by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.45,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,S... Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.30,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange,\Nyou'll do whatever I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:52.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.39,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. You're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,All done. Now open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute! Just like a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.32,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.79,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it bring back memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:37.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were little,\Nwe used to play like this a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.45,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.00,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, you were really cute back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're even cuter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.03,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I look like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.59,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:04.82,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, you'd look so nice if\Nyou had your ears pierced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I pierce them for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.66,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.60,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my plaything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.49,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we change\Nthe look of your hair, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.04,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,A white lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.60,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,White looks good on you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:02.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You once said a white lily\Nis a symbol of virginity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the meaning now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that\Nyou've become an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.96,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:33.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're so beautiful,\NAkira. I really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:40.45,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, this is a secret\Njust between the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.03,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, can you believe that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:58.30,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,All I said was that I\Nwanted to see his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:02.00,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he pushes me in a taxi,\Nand all of a sudden, it's "See ya!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's purely physical...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:06.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he should be able to\Ngrant me a little favor like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:10.35,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya called later or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.98,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he would!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:15.02,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never contacted me!\NNot even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.15,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:18.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't dream\Nof doing such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:22.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never had the ability to be\Ntactful or to care about anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.50,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he would!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never contacted me! Not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:40.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never had the ability to be\Ntactful or to care about anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:52.85,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here to take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave your name and number...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:56.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:02.79,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:12.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought only of you since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I've missed you this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:17.57,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:26.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you,\NI don't feel anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.81,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get laid, then say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.98,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:10.63,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems simple dresses\Nlook better on you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:15.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:16.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.14,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a plaything\Nof me for a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.67,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Shame on you!\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:28.48,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Toys are something you play\Nwith until you're bored of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.31,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:34.65,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting so beautiful that\Nyou're afraid of yourself, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:39.62,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid, but it's\Nnot because I'm beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:44.69,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid, because I look more\Nand more like you every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:47.82,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:52.79,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Play with me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.80,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be bored with me yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.71,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say "I love you" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:10.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Just your body is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.38,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your heart, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:18.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:19.80,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:21.31,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:27.90,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to feel your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:31.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be your heart.\NYour body is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:34.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have sex\Nwith me for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:40.68,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Until it ends,\Nyou'll be mine and mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:07.40,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:09.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:34.92,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So... so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.80,0:25:44.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.34,0:25:49.14,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,going to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.74,0:25:54.14,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.89,0:26:09.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.27,0:26:21.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... looks like Amemiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.32,0:26:36.45,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here to take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:42.09,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave your name, number\Nand message at the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.70,0:26:47.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, how have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.30,0:26:50.03,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.07,0:26:54.40,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:56.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were home!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.94,0:26:58.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.74,0:27:01.47,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. It seems I may be\Nhome sometime in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.95,0:27:03.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to see you soon, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.98,0:27:04.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.68,0:27:07.67,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,His sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.42,0:27:10.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see you, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:11.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!?
